quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  14,6,"(JaŇčto) tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen: "ciftoree dokke Alla on e moo…óon, tuma o da…óndunoo on e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe no defaynoo on lepte bon¬ī…óe. He…ďe kirsa …ďi…ó…ďe mon (wor…ďe) …ďe ngacca (…ďi…ó…ďe) mon rew…ďe. Wonii e …óuum mo'on, jarrabuyee maw…óo immorde ka Joomi mon","
  14,7,"e tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo: "Pellet si on njettii, ma mi …ďeydan on. Si on njeddii non, pellet lepte am …óeen ko ca…ótu…óe"."
  14,8,"Muusaa maaki: "Si on njeddii, onon e won…ďe ka leydi …ďen fow, [ngnndon] pellet Alla ko Galo jettinii…óo"."
  14,9,"E kumpite …ďeen adinoo…ďe on araani on, yim…ďe Nuuhu e Aadi, e Samuuda e …ďeen wonunoo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď- …ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa Alla? Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, …ďe ndutti juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen ka kunndule ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbii: "minen min yed- dii ko nulida…óon e mun kon, minen, mi…óen e cikkitii e ko noddoton men e mun sikkitii…ďe"."
  14,10,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen maaki: "E hara sikke no e fii Alla, pu…ó…óu…óo kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin, homo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e bakkatuuji mon, homo nee…ďnana on haa e lajal innaangal?" ∆Āe mbi'i: "On ngonaani si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru amen. Ho…óon faandii nde sakkoto…óon(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraa…ďe amen ndewatnoo. ngaddanee amen hujja …ďanngu…óo"."